            "summary": "Solvency Capital Requirement - General Provisions 3.3 requires that the Solvency Capital Requirement mu",
            "as_at_date": "31/12/2024"
          },
          {
            "paragraph_number": "2.2",
            "summary": "Firms should include these risks in their internal model, unless it can be demonstrated that these are not material. Failure to include material risks within the scope of the internal model will mean ",
